title: Flight Simulator 2020 - PMDG DC6 - Build 36 released
description:
PMDG has released another update for their DC6. It is the 2nd update after Sim Update 5 was released and contains fixes and enhancements in the following categories:

- external model
- system behavior/functionality
- virtual cockpit

If you also want to give the aircraft a try you can download it from the site below:
https://pmdg.com/pmdg-dc-6-for-msfs/
